## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run build` to verify Next.js route compilation.
- `npx tsc --noEmit` to ensure no TypeScript type errors in the new pages and components.

### Manual Verification
- Visual inspection of all 11 pages in the development server (`npm run dev`).
- Ensure all pages adhere to the design system (Premium, clean, Stripe/Airbnb-like).
- Verify responsive behavior on mobile (375px viewport).
- Test mock data rendering across different pages.
